function CharacterSearch(props) {
  return (
    <form className='form__search'>
      <label className='form__search--labelName' htmlFor='name'>
        ¿Que personaje quieres ver?
      </label>
      <input
        className='form__search--inputName'
        type='text'
        name='name'
        id='name'
        value={props.searchName}
        onChange={handleSearchName}
      />

      <label className='form__search--labelSelect' htmlFor='selectSearch'>
        Filtros:
      </label>
      <select
        className='form__search--inputSearch'
        name='selectSearch'
        id='selectSearch'
      >
        <option value='all'>Ordeandos alfabéticamente</option>
        <option value='specie'>Especie</option>
        <option value='origin'>Planeta de origen</option>
      </select>
    </form>
  );
}
export default CharacterSearch;
